Interface MyList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MyListImpl

    public interface MyList
extends java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>
    Provides implementing classes with a least number of methods which allow to use these classes as a lists. Suggets that implementing class has internal structure which can be considered as a linked list of elements. This interface contains methods for adding, removing and checking of presence of elements in the list and also some methods for representing the list or information about it.
    Version:
    1.0, 13 Nov 2017
    Author:
    Hrynevych Pavlo
